These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, folk, r&b, reggae, soul
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, alhambra, dannemann, tiparillo, pall-mall, ritmeester
 1. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5
 3. the fan of reggae is not the pall-mall-smoker##6
 4. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5
 5. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5
 6. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the right of the dannemann-smoker##5
 7. the pall-mall-smoker is not the fan of dubstep##6
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of blues is somewhere between the ritmeester-smoker and the fan of r&b##7
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
11. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the siglo-smoker##5
12. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##5
13. the siglo-smoker is the fan of blues##1
14. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the left of the fan of reggae##5
15. the fan of soul is the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | blues | folk   | soul     | dubstep    | reggae   |
| Cigar           | pall-mall | siglo   | ritmeester | tiparillo | dannemann | alhambra |

