.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: disaster, documentary, drama, fantasy, horror, time-travel
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: september, april, october, july, december, june
 1. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 7. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
 8. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching horror movies is not the person who's birthday is in december##6
10. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in july##7
11. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
13. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
14. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4
15. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
16. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
17. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person watching horror movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | time-travel | fantasy | horror     | drama      | disaster |
| Birthday           | april         | october        | december   | july | september | june    |

