.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
6 different pets are kept: turtle, goldfish, mouse, pony, dog, lizard
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, lacrosse, parkour, surfing, swimming
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is not the owner of the pony##6
 5. the owner of the turtle is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 8. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
10. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the owner of the dog and the owner of the goldfish##7
11. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
13. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
14. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Pet   | dog        | pony | lizard    | turtle    | mouse | goldfish |
| Sport      | basketball | surfing  | swimming | parkour | baseball | lacrosse      |

