 3. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the davidoff-smoker is not the person drinking mirinda##6
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking mirinda##7
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking water##7
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking lemonade##7
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the davidoff-smoker##5
13. the montecristo-smoker is the person drinking lemonade##1
14. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
