 2. the person who's sport is climbing is the dressmaker##1
 3. the police-officer is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
 4. the entrepreneur is somewhere between the police-officer and the person who's sport is weightlifting##7
 5. the paramedic is somewhere between the musician and the entrepreneur##7
 6. the dancer is somewhere to the right of the police-officer##5
 7. the dancer is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 8. the police-officer is on the right of the paramedic##1
 9. the dressmaker is somewhere to the right of the musician##5
10. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
11. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
12. the dressmaker is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
13. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |
| Job   | musician | paramedic | police-officer   | entrepreneur  | dancer      | dressmaker  |
| Sport         | rugby      | baseball | handball | water-polo | weightlifting | climbing |

