.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-19::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: woodworking, drawing, hiking, photography, cooking, writing
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, skateboard, train, tram, trike
 1. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
 5. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person driving the boat##2
 7. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
11. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
