.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: camping, collecting, drawing, photography, traveling, video-games
6 different games are played: bridge, chess, billiard, domino, go, mah-jongg
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere between the person playing domino and the person playing chess##7
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person playing go##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
 8. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 9. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5
10. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
11. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
14. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
15. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | drawing         | photography | collecting | camping   | video-games | traveling  |
| Game     | go | domino  | billiard  | mah-jongg | chess  | bridge |

 